Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:40.67,EDCN,,0,0,680,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}有一天 在上锁的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:43.26,EDCN,,0,0,680,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}这个漆黑的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:46.05,EDCN,,0,0,680,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}将所有苦涩的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:48.05,EDCN,,0,0,680,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}全都尘封于此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:52.23,EDCN,,0,0,680,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}就像编织Fiction一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:54.85,EDCN,,0,0,680,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}用上MP的话
